(1, '2009-04-15', 'Cocoon', 'Dinner Party', '', '', 'London', '65 Regent Street', '', 'London', 'W1B 4EA', '27 - 42', '7.00', 60, 'Cocoon is an exquisite, futuristic designed venue in the heart of the West End. One of the leading Pan-Asian restaurants in London, Cocoon offers a sublime selection of dishes as well as a vibrant champagne bar and cocktail lounge. The expertly prepared recipes blends perfectly the ancient cooking techniques of Japan, China and Thailand.\r\n\r\n', 'Event Sold Out', 'cocoon1.jpg', 0, 0),
(2, '2009-05-07', 'Asia De Cuba', 'Dinner Party', '', '', 'London', 'St Martin''s Lane Hotel, 45 St Martin''s Lane', '', 'London', 'WC2N 4HX', '27 - 42', '7.30', 65, 'Be wowed by Philippe Starck’s jaw-dropping, contemporary interior at Asia de Cuba, in St Martin''s Lane Hotel. The atmosphere here is buzzing, and the menu broad with a huge range of tempting Asian and latin fusion dishes, including an imaginative vegetarian menu. Those with a sweet-tooth will be wowed by the desserts. \r\n\r\nTicket includes 2 courses with wine\r\n\r\n \r\n', 'Event Sold Out', 'asiadecuba.jpg', 0, 0),
(3, '2009-04-30', 'Taman Gang', 'Networking Drinks', '', '', 'London', '141 Park Lane', 'Mayfair', 'London', 'W1K 7AA', '27 - 42', '7.15', 25, 'Please join us for our monthly networking drinks at Taman Gang in Mayfair, a Balinese-inspired bar and certainly one of the most exotic bars in London. Taman Gang is pure luxury and attracts a stylish crowd. From 11pm, Taman Gang''s resident DJ will arrive for those of you who want to continue partying. ', 'Event Sold Out', 'tamangang.jpg', 0, 0),
