(22, '2009-07-02', 'The Collection', 'Networking Drinks', '', '', 'London', '264 Brompton Road,', 'South Kensington', '', 'SW3 2AS', '27 - 42', '7.30', 25, 'Make a model entrance along the 80ft lit catwalk which must be one of the most glamorous entrances to any restaurant in London. \r\n\r\nThe ambience of these bar is perfect for networking and meeting other like-minded single Asian professionals, whilst also enjoying a great selection of stunning cocktails. \r\n\r\nTicket price includes glass of wine on arrival.\r\n', 'Event Sold Out', 'thecollection.jpg', 0, 0),
(23, '2009-07-09', 'Suka@The Sanderson Hotel', 'Dinner Party', '', '', 'London', '50 Berners St', '', 'London', 'W1T 3NG', '27 - 42', '7.30', 55, 'For summer, we are hosting a dinner party at Suka, at the stunning Sanderson Hotel in London.This restaurant offers modern authentic Malaysian cuisine prepared with European sensibility. \r\n\r\nOur dinner parties are informal and fun and definitely one not to be missed, especially this one at Suka.\r\nDinner includes 2 courses with wine.', 'Available', 'sukathesandersonhotel.jpg', 0, 0),
(24, '2009-06-18', 'Sketch', 'Networking Drinks', '', '', 'London', ' 9 Conduit Street', 'Mayfair', 'London', 'W1S 2XG', '27 - 42', '7.30', 25, 'Please join us for our monthly Networking drinks at the uber-cool Sketch Bar in London''s Mayfair.\r\n\r\nTwo expansive floors of a converted 18th century site in Conduit Street, Mayfair. A Grade II listed building, it was formerly the headquarters of both RIBA and Christian Dior.\r\n\r\nThis is truly a unique bar to host the start of the Summer season, and will no doubt be sold out quickly so don''t delay in booking your tickets.', 'Event Sold Out', 'sketch.jpg', 0, 0),
(25, '2009-07-30', 'Mews of Mayfair', 'Networking Drinks', '', '', 'London', '10-11 Lancashire Court,', 'Mayfair', 'London', 'W1S 1EY', '27 - 42', '7.30', 25, 'Our last Networking drinks event before we close for Summer will be at this super-stylish boutique bar located within an historic cobbled courtyard in the heart of London. This is truly London''s best kept secret...until now. Limited tickets available. Ticket price includes glass of wine on arrival.', 'Event Sold Out', 'mewsofmayfair.jpg', 0, 0),
(31, '2009-10-15', 'Mews of Mayfair', 'Networking Drinks', '', '', 'London', '10 Lancashire Court', '', 'London', 'W1S 1EY', '27 - 42', '7.30', 25, 'We hope you can join us for our monthly Networking drinks at this gorgeous bar in the heart of Mayfair. Tucked at the end of a cobbeld mews, this lounge bar is London''s best kept secret...until now. Drinks reception will be held between 7.30 and 8.15pm.', 'Event Sold Out', 'mewsofmayfair0.jpg', 0, 0),
(27, '2009-08-20', 'Long Bar - Sanderson Hotel', 'Networking Drinks', '', '', 'London', '50 Berners Street', '', 'London', 'W1T 3NG', '27 - 42', '7.30', 25, 'At about 80ft long, the Sanderson''s Long Bar is appropriately named. The dramatic, onyx Long Bar is the focal point for energy at Sanderson. Our Networking drinks will start at this bar and then move to the Terrace....a perfect venue for a Summer''s evening. Ticket price includes glass of wine on aarival.', 'Event Sold Out', 'longbarsandersonhotel0.jpg', 0, 0),
(32, '2009-10-29', 'Bedford and Strand', 'Networking Drinks', '', '', 'London', '1a Bedford Street', '', 'London', 'WC2E 9HH', '27 - 42', '7.30', 45, 'Please join us for our Cheese and Wine party at this lovely bar in Covent Garden. The evening will start with the group sampling 6 wines with 6 cheeses, with a short introduction by Bedford and Strand staff on the selections they have chosen for us. We will then move onto networking and socialising, before we finish the evening with a chocolate dessert accompanied by a dessert wine. \r\n\r\nThis is  a unique and fun event so please don’t leave it to the last minute to book your ticket.', 'Event Sold Out', 'bedfordandstrand.jpg', 0, 0),
(28, '2009-09-24', 'Collection Bar', 'Networking Drinks', '', '', 'London', '264 Brompton Road', '', 'London', 'SW3 2AS', '27 - 42', '7.30', 25, 'The moment you enter along the 80-ft catwalk (The Collection is based in a converted fashion warehouse), you know you’re somewhere to see and be seen. The ambiance in this bar is amazing so don''t miss out on this month''s Networking drinks.', 'Event Sold Out', 'collectionbar.jpg', 0, 0),
(29, '2009-09-10', 'Sketch Bar, Mayfair', 'Networking Drinks', '', '', 'London', '9 Conduit Street', '', 'London', 'W1S 2XG', '27 - 42', '7.30', 25, 'Sketch Bar in the heart of Mayfair is a complex and unique venue that has attracted unprecedented media reaction for its myriad food, drink and entertainment styles since it opened in December 2002. Be wowed by the architecture and super-glamorous ambiance over informal Networking drinks. \r\n', 'Event Sold Out', 'sketchbarmayfair.jpg', 0, 0),
(30, '2009-10-08', 'Asia De Cuba', 'Dinner Party', '', '', 'London', '45 St Martins Lane,', '', 'London', 'WC2N 4HX', '27 - 42', '7.30', 60, 'This month''s dinner party will be hosted at Asia De Cuba, at St Martin''s Lane Hotel, Covent Garden. The restaurant combines elements of Asian and Cuban cuisine served sharing-style in a high energy, super-chic restaurant. Considering that 62% of daters list "similar dining habits" as their top compatibility trait, it''s clear to see why our dinner parties are always booked up quickly.\r\n', 'Event Sold Out', 'asiadecuba0.jpg', 0, 0),
(33, '2009-11-13', 'Home House', 'Networking Drinks', '', '', 'London', '21 Portman Square', 'Marylebone', 'London', 'W1H 6LW', '27 - 42', '7.30', 25, 'Home House is a former London abode of the Countess of Home and is exquisitely beautiful and has been lovingly restored to its former glory. This private members club behind Selfridges attracts young, stylish and affluent people from London and overseas and being so exclusive, we felt this was a great venue for our Networking drinks. We provide an excellent opportunity for you to meet other Asian professionals in London. Limited tickets available so please book soon to avoid disappointment. Drinks reception will start at 7.30pm until 8.15pm.', 'Event Sold Out', 'homehouse.jpg', 0, 0),
(36, '2009-12-13', 'Christmas @ Home House', 'Christmas Lunch', '', '', 'London', '20 Portman Square', 'Marylebone', 'London', 'W1H 6LW', '27 - 42', '12.30', 45, 'Please join us for our Christmas lunch at Home House, former London abode of the Countess of Home. This private members club behind Selfridges attracts young, stylish and affluent people from London and overseas and being so exclusive, we felt this was a great venue for our 3 course Christmas lunch. Off course the menu will include a traditional turkey roast with all the trimmings but if you are looking for lighter option, they will be available too.', 'Female Tickets Sold Out', 'christmashomehouse.jpg', 19, 0),
(41, '2010-01-28', 'Mews of Mayfair', 'Networking Drinks', '', '', 'London', '10-11 Lancashire Court', 'Mayfair', '', 'W1S 1EY', '27 - 42', '7.15', 25, 'We hope you can join us for our first Networking drinks event in 2010 at Mews, one of Mayfair’s best-kept secrets: a sophisticated four-floor restaurant and bar with an air of exclusivity and chic style.\r\n \r\nTucked away in a historic courtyard, the converted mews houses offer a venue that’s as smart and stylish as its location – the very heart of Mayfair. Our drinks events are very popular and are booked up quickly so please don''t leave it to the last minute to book your ticket.', 'Event Sold Out', 'mewsofmayfair2.jpg', 0, 0),
(34, '2009-11-26', 'Carbon Bar @ Cumberland Hotel', 'Networking Drinks', '', '', 'London', 'Cumberland Hotel, Old Quebec Street', 'Marylebone', 'London', 'W1C 1LZ', '27 - 42', '7.30', 25, 'The spacious bar in this ultra-glamourous hotel attracts the affluent professionals and the super-stylish. Our drinks events are not to be missed, especially our first time holding drinks at Carbon Bar.\r\n\r\nDrinks reception is between 7.30pm and 8.15pm so please arrive early ', 'Event Sold Out', 'carbonbarcumberlandhotel.jpg', 0, 0),
(35, '2009-12-11', 'Fifth Floor bar @ Harvey Nichols', 'Networking Drinks', '', '', 'London', 'Harvey Nichols, 109 - 125 Knightsbridge', '', ' London', 'SW1 7RJ', '27 - 42', '7.30', 25, 'Please join us for our Xmas drinks at the top of this stunning department store in Knightsbridge. This seems to be the perfect place to end a very busy year for Asian Dinner Club. The drinks reception will be from 7.30pm to 8.15pm.', 'Event Sold Out', 'fifthfloorbarharveynichols.jpg', 0, 2),
(42, '2010-02-11', 'Quaglinos', 'Valentines Dinner', '', '', 'London', '16 Bury Street', '', 'London', 'SW1Y 6AJ', '27 - 42', '7.00', 60, 'Following a successful Valentines dinner at Quaglino''s in 2009, we have decided to come back. The food is delicious, the atmosphere is buzzing and therefore makes this a great place to host an informal dinner party for our members. Limited tickets available.', 'Female Tickets Sold Out', 'quaglinos.jpg', 18, 0),
(37, '2009-12-17', 'Palm Beach Casino', 'Networking Drinks', '', '', 'London', '30 Berkeley street', 'Mayfair', '', 'W1J 8EH', '27 - 42', '7.30', 25, 'Located in the heart of Mayfair, the Palm Beach Casino features one of the largest gaming rooms in London. \r\n\r\nIts high ceilings offer a true feeling of space and elegance, complete with real palm trees.\r\n\r\nThis is our last Networking drinks until the New Year and we do hope you can join us for a drinks and maybe a flutter!\r\n\r\nThis is a great way to meet other single Asian professionals in London.', 'Event Sold Out', 'mewsofmayfair1.jpg', 0, 0),
(40, '2010-01-14', 'The Arts Club, Mayfair', 'Dinner Party', '', '', 'London', '40 Dover Street', 'Mayfair', '', 'W1S 4NP', '27 - 42', '7.30', 60, 'The Arts Club in Mayfair is an exclusive private member''s Club who have invited Asian Dinner Club members to experience an evening of "Fine Dining and Fine Art". This unique event is a rare opportunity to dine amongst some amazing pieces of art displayed around the dining room. The Arts Club have the finest chefs from some of the best kitchens and we will be sampling 2 courses with wine. Places are very limited so please book early.', 'Event Sold Out', 'theartsclubmayfair.jpg', 0, 1),
(38, '2010-02-20', 'Home House', 'Networking Drinks', '', '', 'London', '21 Portman Square', 'London', '', 'W1H 6LW', '27 - 42', '8.00', 25, 'Please join us at the exclusive Private Member''s Club, Home House, for our Networking drinks event. Our members have requested we hold more events on the weekend so we are expecting a large number of members at this event.', 'Event Sold Out', 'homehouse1.jpg', 0, 0),
(43, '2010-03-11', 'Asia De Cuba', 'Dinner Party', '', '', 'London', '45 St Martins Lane', '', 'London', 'WC2N 4HX', '27 - 42', '7.30', 60, 'Be wowed by Philippe Starck’s jaw-dropping, contemporary interior at Asia de Cuba, in St Martin’s Lane which is a magnet for a young, hip crowd. The atmosphere here is buzzing, and the menu broad with a huge range of tempting Asian and latin fusion dishes, including an imaginative vegetarian menu.This is the third time we are hosting a dinner party here as the others have been so much fun. Don''t leave it too late to book your ticket', 'Event Sold Out', 'asiadecuba1.jpg', 0, 0),
(39, '2010-02-25', 'The Collection Bar', 'Networking Drinks', '', '', 'London', '264 Brompton Road', 'South Kensington', 'London', 'SW3 2AS', '27 - 42', '7.30', 25, 'One of our favourite bars in London, The Collection Bar never fails to disappoint with it''s 80ft lit entrance, super-glamourous crowd and amazing cocktails. This venue is always popular so please don''t leave it to the last minute to book your ticket.', 'Event Sold Out', 'thecollectionbarsouthkensington.jpg', 0, 0),
(51, '2010-05-08', 'Home House', 'Networking Drinks', '', '', 'London', '21 Portman Square', '', 'London', 'W1H 6LW', '27 - 42', '8.00', 25, 'Please join us at one of London''s most luxurious Private Member''s Clubs, Home House for our Networking drinks events. This venue attracts a large number of our members and it''s location in Central London (close to Selfridges) is perfect. Please don''t miss this opportunity to socialise with other single Asians in London. We have our drinks reception between 8-8.30pm with a selection of wines and soft drinks for those who arrive early.', 'Event Sold Out', 'homehouse2.jpg', 0, 0),
(44, '2010-04-10', 'Kumo Knightsbridge', 'Networking Drinks', '', '', 'London', '11 Beauchamp Place', '', 'Knightsbridge', 'SW3 1NQ', '27 - 42', '7.30', 25, 'Kumo is a Japanese restaurant with an amazing bar inthe heart of Knightsbridge near San Lorenzo. It is one of London''s best-kept secrets and definitely one venue to visit for their delicious alcoholic and non-alcoholic cocktails. We are extremely happy to hold April''s Networking Drinks here and request you to book up early for this event so as not to be disappointed.Our drinks reception is between 7.30pm and 8pm where you can have a glass of wine or non-alcoholic drink....only if you arrive early.', 'Event Sold Out', 'kumoknightsbridge.jpg', 0, 0),
(45, '2010-04-16', 'The Avenue', 'Dinner Party', '', '', 'London', '7-9 St James Street', '', 'London', 'SW1A 1EE', '27 - 42', '7.00', 60, 'The Avenue opened in 1995 to great critical and architectural acclaim and the place has the ''wow'' factor that is hard to dispute; it''s big, bright and buzzy. The Avenue is the perfect place to socialise and relax with other single Asian professionals, as well as enjoying good food and wine. Limited spaces available. ', 'Event Sold Out', 'theavenue.jpg', 0, 0),
(46, '2010-04-25', 'The Warrington, Maida Vale', 'Sunday Lunch', '', '', 'London', '93 Warrington Crescent', '', 'London', 'W9  1EH', '27 - 42', '12.30', 45, 'The Warrington is owned by the infamous Gordon Ramsay. It is an immense property and an archetypal British pub with Art Nouveau friezes, marble pillars and a few other elaborate touches to give it an upper-middle class feel. The first floor restaurant offers excellent food and will not disappoint....a perfect way for our members to spend a lazy Sunday and meet other single Asian professionals in a relaxed environment.', 'Event Sold Out', 'thewarringtonmaidavale.jpg', 0, 0),
(47, '2010-03-13', 'Home House', 'Networking Drinks', '', '', 'London', '21 Portman Square', '', 'London', 'W1H 6LW', '27 - 42', '8.00', 25, 'The newly designed bar at 21 Portman Square offers the perfect space to network and socialise with other single Asians in London. This private members club is a fabulous building behind Selfridges and attracts an affluent crowd. Don''t miss this Saturday night event! Limited tickets available.', 'Event Sold Out', 'homehouse0.jpg', 0, 0),
(48, '2010-05-15', 'La Portes des Andes', 'Dinner Party', '', '', 'London', '32 Bryanston Street', '', 'London', 'W1H 7EG', '27 - 42', '8.00', 65, 'Please join us for an exceptional dinner party at the famous Porte des Indes. It is an unforgettable experience, on every level. Opulent and luxurious, it features art, antiques, a marble staircase and nine-metre high waterfall. Tropical plants and flowers adorn the spacious eaterie ï¿½ 5,000 stems are imported each week. As well as classic Indian cuisine, the eight chefs whip up specialities from the former Indian French colonies.\r\n\r\nAfter dinner we will continue the night at Home House, a private member''s Club, minutes walk from this restaurant. This is the first time we are hosting a dinner party on a Saturday night and combining the experience with more socialising at Home House - limited tickets available so please book up soon if you can make this date.', 'Event Sold Out', 'laportesdesandes.jpg', 0, 0),
(49, '2010-04-29', 'Collection Bar, South Kensington', 'Networking Drinks', '', '', 'London', '264 Brompton Road', '', 'South Kensington', 'SW3 2AS', '27 - 42', '7.30', 25, 'In the heart of Chelsea, Collection Bar is a very popular venue with our members as attracts a stylish, fun crowd. This celebrated bar also offers exotic, fatabulous cocktails both alcoholic and non-alcoholic.\r\n\r\nOur drinks reception is between 7.30pm and 8pm where we offer members who arrive early a glass of wine or non-alcoholic drink....so don''t miss out!', 'Female Tickets Sold Out', 'collectionbarsouthkensington.jpg', 20, 0),
(50, '2010-03-25', 'Mayfair Bar @ Mayfair Hotel', 'Networking Drinks', '', '', 'London', 'Stratton Street', '', 'Mayfair', 'W1J 8LT', '27 - 42', '7.30', 25, 'Recently judged the ‘Best Hotel Bar in London’ The May Fair Bar is a stunning and one of the ultra-cool places to be in London. Don''''t miss our drinks here - we have a private area reserved - limited tickets available.', 'Female Tickets Sold Out', 'mayfairbarmayfairhotel.jpg', 14, 0),
(55, '2010-06-24', 'Harvey Nichols 5th Floor Bar', 'Networking Drinks', '', '', 'London', '109-125 Knightsbridge', '', 'London', 'SW1X 7RJ', '27 - 42', '7.30', 25, 'Please join us for drinks at Harvey Nichols 5th Floor Bar which provides a glamorous setting for our members to socialise and network with other single Asian professionals in London. We have a drinks reception between 7.30pm and 8pm where you can enjoy a complimentary glass of wine if you arrive early. This is a popular venue so please book early to avoid disappointment.', 'Female Tickets Sold Out', 'harveynichols5thfloorbar.jpg', 9, 0),
(52, '2010-05-20', 'Mews of Mayfair', 'Networking Drinks', '', '', 'London', '10-11 Lancashire Court', '', 'Mayfair', 'W1S 1EY', '27 - 42', '7.30', 25, 'Please join us for our Networking drinks in May. Mews is one of Mayfairâ€™s best-kept secrets: a sophisticated bar with an air of exclusivity. Tucked away in a historic courtyard, the converted mews houses offer a venue thatâ€™s as smart and stylish as its location â€“ the very heart of Mayfair. This is always a popular venue so please book up early to avoid disappointment. Free glass of wine or soft drink if you arrive between 7.30pm and 8.30pm.', 'Event Sold Out', 'mewsofmayfair3.jpg', 0, -1),
(53, '2010-05-28', 'Just St James', 'Networking Drinks', '', '', 'London', '12 St James''s Street', '', 'London', 'SW1A 1ER', '27 - 42', '7.30', 25, 'Just St James is set over three floors with a super-cool lounge bar.It is situated in the heart of St Jamesâ€™s, just off Piccadilly and will be a great place to host one of our Networking drinks event in May. Please book early to avoid disappointment.', 'Female Tickets Sold Out', 'juststjames.jpg', 17, 0),
(54, '2010-06-11', 'Gilgamesh', 'Dinner Party', '', '', 'London', 'Stables Market, ', '', 'Chalk Farm Road, London', 'NW1 8AH', '27 - 42', '7.15', 65, 'Celebrity chef Ian Pengelley brings his acclaimed pan-Asian cuisine to this big, bold Babylonian-style space in the Camden.The dining room feels endlessly spacious, thanks to floor-to-ceiling windows and a 40ft-high ceiling with retractable roof.This is the dinner party not to be missed as it has fabulous food, decor and people! We will continue socialising after dinner with drinks in one of it''s many lounge bars.', 'Event Sold Out', 'gilgamesh.jpg', 0, 0),
(60, '2010-07-16', 'The Yacht London', 'Summer Party', '', '', 'London', 'Temple Pier', '', 'Victoria Embankment', 'WC2R 2PN', '27 - 42', '8.00', 60, 'Please join us for our summer party on board The Yacht London, a 1920s steam vessel moored at Temple Pier. Our members will enjoy canapes and complimentary drinks until 10pm after which you can network and socialise in either the stunning Art Deco cocktail lounge or the champagne bar on the top deck. This is the party not to be missed this summer so please book early to avoid disappointment.\r\n\r\nNote: there will be a TV screen for those who want to keep an eye on the World Cup match showing that evening', 'Available', 'theyachtlondon.jpg', 45, 37),
